WEBVTT

00:00:00.196 --> 00:00:04.036
We all have questions
that keep us up at night.

00:00:04.076 --> 00:00:05.316
Here are two of mine.

00:00:06.756 --> 00:00:09.156
The first is: What makes us human?

00:00:10.756 --> 00:00:13.956
In a world where
human beings and technology

00:00:13.996 --> 00:00:16.716
are increasingly converging

00:00:16.756 --> 00:00:19.356
and where with the power
of virtual reality

00:00:19.356 --> 00:00:22.476
we can embody anything we want,

00:00:22.516 --> 00:00:24.876
what is it that continues
to keep us human?

00:00:26.516 --> 00:00:28.716
Now there's loads
of different answers to this,

00:00:28.756 --> 00:00:30.476
but the social anthropologist in me